<TEXT>
<P>
 West Hollywood is putting sculpture on display in an unlikely location: the 
Santa Monica Boulevard median strip. 
</P>
<P>
 Through Sept. 30, the median will be the site of "Mutable Existence," an 
exhibit of works by Pascal Giacomini, a French-born artist living in Los 
Angeles. 
</P>
