<TEXT>
<P>
 Machinists Union Sued Over UAL Buyout Role: A class-action suit filed in U.S. 
District Court in Chicago asks for a new vote by the union's members on 
participating in the proposed $4.9-billion employee buyout of UAL Corp., United 
