<HEADLINE>
<P>
WORLD CUP USA '94 / THE FIRST ROUND; FACTS AND FIGURES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 GROUP F at Washington 
</P>
<P>
 Saudi Arabia: 1 
</P>
